skin-a54b82c79b59_2_st.name: ★ StatTrak™ Butterfly Knife | Forest DDPAT (Field-Tested)

This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

This is a custom-designed balisong, commonly known as a butterfly knife.
